des an in-depth understanding of the origin of coherent rotation in\nconfined tissues, and extracts useful insights into the influence of various\nphysical parameters on the pattern of such movements\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2015 12:58:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Jan 2016 18:08:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-10"}
